          <p
            style="color:#666666;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:15px;"
          >
            You have received a new message from
            <strong>{{adminName}}</strong>.
          </p>
          <p
            style="color:#666666;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0;"
